        <itemProvenance>This item was acquired new, roughly 2006-2007, when Konijn was a child. The item was briefly lost after being stolen from Konijn while at a TCG tournament in the late 2000s, but was recovered shortly thereafter when Konijn recognized the condition of the screen protector at the local secondhand games store while trying to obtain a replacement. Quote from Konijn: “[T]he people from the shop felt real bad about it and assured us the kids who stole my ds were never welcome there again, and my dad bought my ds back for the same price they'd bought it off of the kids as a gesture of good will.”</itemProvenance>
        <collectTitle>Robbie Konijn’s Nintendo console collection (2006-2025)</collectTitle>
